content: What are all the medications you are currently taking, including over-the-counter drugs and supplements?
Do you have any known drug allergies?
Have you had any surgeries in the past?
Can you estimate how many Extra Strength Tylenol pills (325mg each) or Tylenol PM pills (500mg acetaminophen) you were taking per day during that period?
Have you experienced any abdominal pain, particularly in your upper right side, or have you noticed any changes in the color of your urine or stools?
Does the itching get worse at any particular time of day or night, or after eating certain foods?
Is the jaw pain still present, or has it completely resolved since you stopped taking the Tylenol?
